search::addLink()

Description
    public void search::addLink(array $attPairs)

Parameters
    attPairs
    An array containing a name/value pair.

Examples
    <?php
	$s = new search($engine);
        $s->relevanceSearch = TRUE;
	$link = array();
	$link['table1'] = $engine->dbTables("traditionalReserves");
	$link['field1'] = "ID";
	$link['table2'] = $engine->dbTables("traditionalReservesLocations");
	$link['field2'] = "trID";
	$s->addLink($link);
	unset($link);
	...
    ?>

See Also
    search::addField()
